definition: general facial appearance/features/arrangement/sequence of ideas/logic (of writing)/rough sketch or general idea of things
progress/prospect of solution/sign of positive outcome
to make sheep eyes at/to cast amorous glances at
to begin to take shape/to be about to materialize

sentences.chinese: 這樣的指望已漸有眉目。

sentences.english: By the summer, Kearns had built a working model of his invention.
sentences.chinese: 夏天的時候，卡恩斯的發明已經有些眉目了。

sentences.english: His papers were always neatly docketed.
sentences.chinese: 他的論文總是附有眉目清楚的摘要。

sentences.english: It was a long time before we seemed to make progress.
sentences.chinese: 好長時間後，我們才似乎有了點兒眉目。

sentences.english: My father turns toward me, eyebrows lifted in surprise.
sentences.chinese: 我爸爸向我轉過身，驚訝地揚起眉目。

sentences.english: Her face is too thin; her complexion has no brilliancy; and her features are not at all handsome.
sentences.chinese: 她的臉太瘦，皮膚沒有光澤，眉目也不清秀。

sentences.english: Response: We are hoping to have an idea of whether the drug has promise within a year.
sentences.chinese: 我們希望在一年以內對此藥是否有前途有個眉目。

sentences.english: That matter is settling into shape.
Her eyes spoke to him at the party.
sentences.chinese: 在宴會上她對他眉目傳情。

sentences.english: However, some light is now being shed on this.
sentences.chinese: 現在，我們有一些眉目了。

sentences.english: Mommy was released from the hospital, but Chang An survey AI things or not.
sentences.chinese: 媽媽快出院了，可常安調查AI的事還是沒有眉目。

sentences.english: He tried in a hundred ways to convey his own feelings, casting arch glances at them.
sentences.chinese: 他乘機百般撩撥，眉目傳情。

sentences.english: Her brother is a tall good-looking young man.
sentences.chinese: 她的哥哥是一位眉目清秀的年輕男士。

sentences.english: I thought the one with real and distinct eyes and eyebrows standing before me, is exactly my friend.
sentences.chinese: 我覺得這個眉目清晰的女人，纔是我真正的朋友。

sentences.english: After months of discussion, a peace agreement is gradually taking shape.
sentences.chinese: 經過幾個月的商討，和平協議漸漸有了眉目。

definition: to have bright eyes and white teeth
the flat area of forehead between the eyebrows/glabella
